    "title": "Peptides in Recovery: Scientific Insights for Researchers",
    "excerpt": "Learn about peptides in recovery, types studied for muscle repair, mechanisms of action, regulatory guidelines, and safety considerations for research.",
    "category": "Research Peptides",
